      • runEngine

        protected void runEngine(IEngineSetup setup,
                         IEngineContext engineContext)
                  throws EngineException
        Runs the engine.
        The default implementation steps are as follows:
        1. Set up the engine by calling buildUpEngine(IEngineSetup, IEngineContext).
        2. Start up the engine by calling startupEngine(IEngineContext).
        3. Run the main loop by calling loop(IEngineContext, IEngineLooper).
        4. Shut down the engine by calling shutdownEngine(IEngineContext), after terminate() has been called or the looper has stopped. 5. Tear down the engine by calling tearDownEngine(IEngineSetup, IEngineContext).

        Generally this method will not return until the engine should exit.

        Parameters:
        setup -
        engineContext -
        Throws:
        EngineException - If an error occurs during execution.
